Title: AN ACT CHANGING THE NAME OF THE MUNICIPAL DISTRICT OF DALIG, PROVINCE OF ISABELA, TO THAT OF "AURORA."
Data:
[ Commonwealth Act No. 572, June 08, 1940 ]
AN ACT CHANGING THE NAME OF THE MUNICIPAL DISTRICT OF DALIG, PROVINCE OF ISABELA, TO THAT OF "AURORA."
Be it enacted by the National Assembly of the Philippines:
Section 1. The name of the municipal district of Dalig, Province of Isabela, is changed to that of "Aurora.ℒαwρhi৷"
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Enacted, without Executive Approval, June 8, 1940.
